name: Collection - Fairytale World
description:
Hey everyone, I am the first one from the fairy world to say hi to the real world. My name's Will, 2 years old, a vegetarian dinosaur. 
I was suppose to give a brief introduction of our world, but I just heard that my buddy got some fresh gingko back, I can't wait to taste! See you next time and wish all of you have a wonderful Monday! 
Oh btw we don't work on Monday, instead we work 2 days in a week, which are Saturday and Sunday, Monday to Friday are our days off ;)
